thread.title_full: TapeOnline reviewed by Roy H. Wagner ASC

author: Roy H. Wagner ASC
title: Roy H. Wagner ASC
text:
This company was recommended to me. What I was ordering might have been old b stock material but it was brand new and of the highest quality. I've placed my second order and two days later I received without additional shipping expense. These are owners that are proud of the service they provide. I cannot recommend them high enough.
Roy H. Wagner ASC
director of photography
